title: Is it Worth it to You?
itunes:title: Is it Worth it to You?
description:
Episode 544 - One of the most important questions you can ask yourself is "does it serve me?" This relationship, this job, this mindset, does it serve me? Because if it doesn't then there is no room for it in your life. We get a finite amount of energy each day and to spend it on something that doesn't move you forward is a complete waste. In this episode, I will talk about this subject and teach you how to get rid of the things that don't serve you in your life.
